text: Clarence Benjamin Wonnacott (31 December 1909 – 1989) was an English professional footballer who played in the Football League for Mansfield Town and Northampton Town. ==References== Category:1909 births Category:1989 deaths Category:English footballers Category:Association football forwards Category:English Football League players Category:Mansfield Town F.C. players Category:Northampton Town F.C. players Category:Shelbourne F.C. players Category:Kidderminster Harriers F.C. players
